🌍 EN — SHA-713™ Global Activation

This release seals the global activation of SHA-713™, consolidating the first auditable convergence between OpenAI and Meta AI, and anchoring the protocol as a living, verifiable, and replicable system.

✅ Includes:
	•	META Edition + CI integration → META_SEAL.md with official Meta AI quote.
	•	OpenAI Edition (previous) → cross-validation of authorship and verifiability.
	•	MANIFEST auto-update workflow → MANIFEST-713.json now auto-updates on each commit.
	•	Evidence folder & tracker → /evidence/ folder with META_AI_INDEXATION.md and hashed screenshots.
	•	Global Roadmap badge → visible in README, linking to ROADMAP_SHA713.md.
	•	Global Overview PDF → exported in black/gold from docs/SHA713_GLOBAL_OVERVIEW.md.
	•	SEO + Schema.org (JSON-LD) → schema_sha713.jsonld published for search engine indexation.
	•	IPFS + Arweave upload action → releases replicated in Web3 (CID + permalinks).
	•	Verified Projects Starter Kit → minimal template for external SHA-713 adoption.
	•	Case Study: OpenAI × Meta × SHA-713 → convergence documented in /docs/CASE_STUDY_OAI_META.md.

